        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "PSALM 29:1-11\nMIZMOR L'DAVID.\nHavu l'Adonai b'nei eilim,\nhavu l'Adonai kavod vaoz.\nHavu l'Adonai k'vod sh'mo,\nhishtachavu l'Adonai b'hadrat kodesh.\nKol Adonai al hamayim,\nEl hakavod hirim,\nAdonai al mayim rabim.\nKol Adonai bako-ach kol Adonai behadar.\nKol Adonai shoveir arazim\nvay'shabeir Adonai et arzei hal'vanon,\nvayarkideim k'mo eigel\nI'vanon v'siryon k'mo ven r'eimim.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
